short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Challenge using AI programming tool cursor, write a chrome wallpaper plugin without writing a single line of code
short.zh_CN: 挑战用AI编程工具cursor，不写一行代码，写一个chrome壁纸插件

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AI provides a new possibility for the public, who can produce programs without programming.Let creativity be wireless, thanks to the great AI!
 
The plugin provides a new tab wallpaper, which changes daily and also supports manual refreshing of the wallpaper.
At the same time, it also provides a search box, Support multiple search engines for searching
long.zh_CN:
AI，为大众提供一种新的可能，不会编程，也可以生产程序。让创意无线，感谢伟大的AI！

插件提供了一个新标签页壁纸，每天更换一张壁纸，也支持手动刷新壁纸。
同时还提供搜索框，支持多个搜索引擎搜索功能
